dct_description_sm: From Chinese Government surveys to 1931 and Japanese Government surveys to 1915.
Depths shown by soundings and tints; relief by contours and spot heights.
Includes tidal information, navigational notes, buoy legend.
Shows coasts, low water areas, drainage, roads, railways, city plan, buildings.
